a.html|archive-date=August 19, 2002|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SakuraGB2\">{{cite web|url=http://www.jupiter.co.jp/game/sakura2/sakura2.html|script-title=ja:\u30b5\u30af\u30e9\u5927\u6226\uff27\uff22\uff12\u3000\u30b5\u30f3\u30c0\u30fc\u30dc\u30eb\u30c8\u4f5c\u6226\n|language=Japanese|website=[[Jupiter Corporation]]|access-date=March 31, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20020819061246/http://www.jupiter.co.jp/game/sakura2/sakura2.html|archive-date=August 19, 2002|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"PocketSakura\">{{cite web|url=http://www.jupiter.co.jp/product/game/other/pokesaku.html|script-title=ja:\u30dd\u30b1\u30c3\u30c8\u30b5\u30af\u30e9 - \u682a\u5f0f\u4f1a\u793e\u30b8\u30e5\u30d4\u30bf\u30fc|language=Japanese|website=[[Jupiter Corporation]]|access-date=March 31, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111005224141/http://www.jupiter.co.jp/product/game/other/pokesaku.html|archive-date=October 5, 2011|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"STSrelease\">{{cite web|url=https://www.famitsu.com/game/news/1144974_1124.html|script-title=ja:\u300e\u30b5\u30af\u30e9\u5927\u6226\u7269\u8a9e\u300f\u767a\u58f2\u3092\u8a18\u5ff5\u3057\u3066\u30bb\u30ac\u30c0\u30a4\u30ec\u30af\u30c8\u3067\u591a\u6570\u306e\u30b0\u30c3\u30ba\u3092\u8ca9\u58f2\uff01|language=Japanese|website=[[Famitsu]]|date=December 26, 2003|access-date=May 19, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130807083246/http://www.famitsu.com/game/news/1144974_1124.html|archive-date=August 7, 2013|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SakuraV0info1\">{{cite web|url=http://sakura-taisen.com/archives/game/v-0/htjimeni.html|script-title=ja:\u30b5\u30af\u30e9\u5927\u6226V EPISODE 0\u301c\u8352\u91ce\u306e\u30b5\u30e0\u30e9\u30a4\u5a18\u301c|language=Japanese|website=Sakura Wars V Episode 0 website|access-date=August 4, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150804235003/http://sakura-taisen.com/game/v-0/htjimeni.html|archive-date=August 4, 2015|url-status=live}}</ref>\n