e|website=[[Funimation]]|access-date=April 12, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051208014835/http://www.sakurataisen.tv/|archive-date=December 8, 2005|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SakuraMovieInterview\">{{cite web|url=http://topics.cinematopics.com/archives/15671|script-title=ja:\u6620\u753b\u300e\u30b5\u30af\u30e9\u5927\u6226\u6d3b\u52d5\u5199\u771f\u300f\u5b8c\u6210\u62ab\u9732\u8a66\u5199\u4f1a \u821e\u53f0\u6328\u62f6|language=Japanese|website=CinemaTopics|date=November 30, 2001|access-date=May 15, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180515144723/http://topics.cinematopics.com/archives/15671|archive-date=May 15, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ASCIIproduction\">{{cite web|url=http://ascii.jp/elem/000/000/324/324154/|script-title=ja:\u3053\u308c\u304c\u6700\u5f8c\u306e\u30b5\u30af\u30e9! \u30bb\u30ac\u3001DC\u7248\u300e\u30b5\u30af\u30e9\u5927\u62264\u300f\u3092\u6765\u6625\u767a\u58f2|language=Japanese|website=[[ASCII Media Works]]|date=June 25, 2001|access-date=May 19, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517171703/http://ascii.jp/elem/000/000/324/324154/|archive-date=May 17, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SakuraReleaseInfo\">{{cite web|url=http://www.sakura-taisen.com/archive/sakura_movie/chara_ani.html|script-title=ja:[ \u51ac\u306e\u89d2\u5ddd\u30a2\u30cb\u30e1\u516c\u5f0f\u30b5\u30a4\u30c8\u30aa\u30fc\u30d7\u30f3!! ]|language=Japanese|website=Sakura Wars Website|access-date=May 15, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806103411/http://www.sakura-taisen.com/sakura_movie/chara_ani.html|archive-date=August 6, 2016|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SakuraVGuidebook\">{{cite book|script-title=ja:\u30b5\u30af\u30e9\u5927\u6226\uff36 \uff5e\u3055\u3089\u3070\u611b\u3057\u304d\u4eba\u3088\uff5e \u539f\u753b\uff06\u8a2d\u5b9a\u8cc7\u6599\u96c6|trans-title=Sakura Wars V: Farewell, My Lovely Original Setting and Picture|publisher=[[SB Creative|SoftBank Creative]]|isbn=4-7973-318